    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes four existing implementations of SPIRITS-like services from Korea Telecom, Lucent Technologies, NEC, and Telia in cooperation with Nortel Networks.  SPIRITS-like services are those originating in the Public Switched Telephone Network (PSTN) and necessitating the interactions of the Internet and PSTN.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
